$values.Text: There are two global constants that need to be set for this sequence to work: THIS_OBSERVATORY and RUN_CONTINUOUSLY.
Set THIS_OBSERVATORY to the integer valu that corresponds to your observatory (from down below (e.g. 2 for DSOC_CERAVOLO).
Set RUN_CONTINUOUSLY to 1 to run 24/7 without interruption or 0 to run one night and then exit.
---------- Set need_darks to 1 to have the sequence get darks at the next available window

---------- This variable is only checked at the start of a target. you can't enable or disable in the middle of a target currently ----------
---------- The cycles_completed variable counts the number of nights the sequence has run ----------
